# Read-only API base.
#
# Default (unset): `/api` — Vite's dev server proxies /api to the real API
# (http://localhost:8000), so the front uses its own origin and works both
# locally and from another device on the LAN, with no CORS and no fixed IP.
#
# Only set this if you serve the front from an origin that does NOT have Vite's
# proxy (e.g. a static build served separately), pointing at the API directly:
# VITE_API_BASE=http://<HOST-IP>:8000
